TopicTitle: I can test planet mods for 1.9

Articles.Content:
Give me your planet mods and i can test them to see if they're compatible with 1.9(.1)

EDIT: The mods aren't "Compatible" until the mod maker says they are. i'm just testing to see if they work. Use the version of the mod for the same version of ksp, So if they say its ready for 1.8 but not 1.9/10 use at your own risk
